  * changed behavior of nagios-server listener:
    - if nagios2 is running then perform a reload after changing config
    - if nagios2 is not running then perform a restart only if
      config registry variable nagios/server/autostart=yes

 -- Sönke Schwardt <schwardt@univention.de>  Tue, 24 Jul 2007 13:29:37 +0200

univention-nagios (1.0.0-5) unstable; urgency=low

  * fix rules file

 -- Janis Meybohm <meybohm@univention.de>  Mon, 23 Jul 2007 14:35:53 +0200

