 -- Sönke Schwardt <schwardt@univention.de>  Thu, 29 Mar 2007 16:39:21 +0200

univention-nagios (0.30) unstable; urgency=low

  * call nagios-client join script if installed on master or backup
  * call nagios-client join script in nagios-server postinst again if needed
  * fixed resync mechanism of nagios-client and nagios-server listener
    (now /etc/nagios/nrpe.univention.d and /etc/nagios2/conf.univention.d
     will be deleted and recreated on resync)
  * added missing softlinks of nuvola theme to nagios base theme logo directories
  * don't append host to default univention service checks in
    nagios-server postinst (nagios-client join script will do this later)
  * added custom host icons depending on host role
  * fixed traceback in nagios-server ldap listener while removing hosts
  * nagios-server ldap listener is now able to handle the changes of attribute
    'associatedDomain'

 -- Sönke Schwardt <schwardt@univention.de>  Thu, 22 Mar 2007 15:31:55 +0100

