  * fix nagios service CLI handling

 -- Stefan Gohmann <gohmann@univention.de>  Mon,  8 Jan 2007 15:32:21 +0100

univention-nagios (0.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * client If baseconfig variable nagios/client/allowedhosts is not set
    ldap/master will be written to nrpe.cfg to define "allowed_hosts".
    By default nagios/client/allowedhosts will be empty.
  * server: new dependencies libapache-mod-auth-pam, univention-admin-nagios
  * server: new pam stack
  * server: In postinst a set of default timeperiods and defaultservices will
    be created.
  * server: change automagically permissions of /var/lib/nagios2/rw/nagios.cmd,
    /var/lib/nagios2/rw and /var/lib/nagios2 if nagios/server/checkexternalcmd
    is changed

 -- Sönke Schwardt <schwardt@univention.de>  Fri, 22 Dec 2006 12:06:59 +0100

